title: Gettysburg National Military Park: Park Scenes by Bill Dowling
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Photos & Multimedia     Photo Gallery     Park Scenes by Bill Dowling                Park Scenes by Bill Dowling                    Park Scenes by Bill Dowling   12 Photos  Licensed Battlefield Guide and photographer Bill Dowling has spent countless hours on the battlefield and here offers several of his more interesting photographs.
